Package xyz.msws.nope.checks.movement

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AntiAFK1
    Checks if a player moves their yaw without changing their pitch
    AntiRotate1
    Slightly teleports the player if they aren't moving every so ticks and sees if (after one tick) the player has in fact actually teleported
    AutoWalk1
    Checks if a player sends a chat message while moving
    BHop1
    Checks distances of where the player last touched the ground
    ClonedMovement1
    Checks recent movements, their differences, and flags if there are too many duplicate differences
    ElytraFlight1
    This is suprisingly simple, checks velocity distances
    FastClimb1
    Checks Y differences and flags if they aren't normal
    FastSneak1
    Gets the average speed while a player is sneaking and flags if too high
    Glide1
    Checks if a player's fall velocity is less than the player's previous fall velocity
    InventoryMove1
    Checks for everytime the player clicks within their inventory are on the ground and has moved
    NoWeb1
    Checks the speed in a snapshot of time while in web
    Spider1
    Checks if a player moves vertically up
    Step1
    Compares vertical distances and checks if they're too high
